text: André Gabriel Matias (born 11 September 1987) is a Portuguese football player of Mozambican descent who plays for Almancilense. ==Club career== He made his professional debut in the Segunda Liga for Fátima on 22 January 2011 in a game against Gil Vicente. ==References== ==External links== Category:1987 births Category:People from Portimão Category:Portuguese people of Mozambican descent Category:Living people Category:Portuguese footballers Category:Louletano D.C. players Category:S.C.
